@startuml uml_class_trust
title LLD — trust-service (HTTP + gRPC — proto/trust.proto)
skinparam defaultFontName Helvetica

package "HTTP / gRPC transport" {
  class "Express routes\n(server.ts)" as Http <<Node>>
  class "TrustService\n(grpc-server.ts)" as Grpc <<Node>> {
    FlagListing()
    ReportAbuse()
    SubmitReview()
    SubmitPeerReview()
    GetReputation()
  }
}

package "Application" {
  class "Trust domain\n(reviews / flags / abuse)" as D <<service>>
}

package "Infrastructure" {
  class "Postgres (Prisma)" as R <<repository>>
  class "Kafka consumer\n(processed_events)" as C
}

Http --> D
Grpc --> D
D --> R
C --> D

note bottom of Grpc
  **Contract:** `proto/trust.proto`
  — moderation and reputation; consumers
  use **processed_events** idempotency
  pattern (see infra SQL).
end note

@enduml
